@predikt/fpmm
=============

This package contains the Fixed Product Market Maker (FPMM) and deterministic
factory that Predikt deploys on-chain for its Conditional-Tokens prediction
markets.

Origin
------

The Solidity sources in `contracts/` are derived from Gnosis'
"conditional-tokens-market-makers" project:

