Modifications by Predikt
------------------------

Predikt has rebranded the package surface (package.json name -> @predikt/fpmm,
README) and added a Foundry build configuration (foundry.toml) so the contracts
compile with `forge` using solc 0.5.x. The build was scoped to the FPMM +
deterministic-factory contracts that Predikt deploys.

The AMM pricing logic (calcBuyAmount, calcSellAmount, buy, sell, addFunding,
removeFunding, and the fee-pool accounting) is UNCHANGED from the upstream
Gnosis implementation. No market-making math was reimplemented or altered.

Deployment model
----------------

These contracts are compiled and deployed as standalone on-chain smart
contracts. The Predikt application interacts with the deployed contracts via
their ABI (JSON-RPC calls); the LGPL-3.0 Solidity sources are not linked into
or bundled with the application binary. The deployed contract remains available
under LGPL-3.0.

